snippet.title: Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Dual Destinies - Turnabout Reclaimed DLC trailer
snippet.description:
ATTORNEY, AHOY! "Turnabout Reclaimed," the all-new DLC case for Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Dual Destinies, is now available in the Nintendo 3DS eShop as well as on iPad, iPhone, and iPod!

Download the first episode for FREE right here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id882362024

Subscribe to the Official Capcom Unity Channel: 
http://bit.ly/Qjb2MV
